Java JDK, JRE, and JVM - Quick Revision Notes

ğŸ”¹ Java Development Kit (JDK)
â€¢	Full form: Java Development Kit
â€¢	Use: Used by developers to write, compile, and run Java programs.
â€¢	Contains:
o	Java Compiler (javac)
